com.google.appinventor.client.widgets.properties

Class EditableProperty

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.google.appinventor.client.properties.Property
      • com.google.appinventor.client.widgets.properties.EditableProperty

  • public final class EditableProperty
extends Property
    Property for display in a PropertiesPanel.

    Such properties have an associated PropertyEditor, hence the name of this class.

    • Field Summary

      Fields 
      Modifier and Type Field and Description
      static int TYPE_INVISIBLE
      Properties of this type will not be displayed in the properties panel.
      static int TYPE_NONPERSISTED
      Properties of this type will not be persisted to the source file upon saving.
      static int TYPE_NORMAL
      Properties of this type will be persisted to the source file upon saving and will be displayed in the properties panel.
